lead_paragraph: Pyeongchang's 2018 Winter Olympics contracts are clean and not "contaminated" by outside factors, the Games' organizing chief told Reuters on Tuesday, as South Korea's sporting community is dragged deeper into a political influence-peddling scandal.

headline.print_headline: Olympics-2018 Games Chief Says Contracts Clean, as Scandal Bleeds Into Sport
